content: What a surreal moment, I just got the COVID-19 vaccine this morning! I will continue to wear a mask and practice social distancing, I can't wait for everyone to get access to the vaccine and for our lives to go back to normal #CovidVaccine #PfizerBioNTech @BrighamWomens
date: 7:09 AM · Dec 19, 2020 from Brigham and Women's Hospital·Twitter for Android
